item.title: Goals
item.description: I have a few different goals with this blog. 1. Improve my writing skills. (Realistic) This is the number one goal. How am I doing this? By writing a lot. This post will come up just one day after my intro post. I don’t have plans to necessarily write everyday, but I will ride whatever wave comes my way. For now, I think every day is sustainable as I am currently on winter break from my MBA classes at West Texas A&M University.
